videos.description: Bol Bol shows off the range as he sinks a pair of 3-point jumpers.
videos.headline: Bol Bol knocks down 2 deep 3-pointers

videos.description: Bol Bol knocks down a 3-pointer from the top of the arc to give him 27 points and a new career high with Oregon.
videos.headline: Bol Bol's 3-ball gives him new career-high 27 points

videos.description: Derrick Bruce  blows by an Oregon defender for an easy layup as Texas Southern upsets No. 18 Oregon.
videos.headline: Texas Southern's Bruce crosses up defender for bucket
